;I am running out of space to write though.. I may need more notebooks.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429943597";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299435863";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331904;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331904";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:151:"&quot;Ohoh! Hang on!&quot; She hops up and dashes over to one of her workbenches, going to one of the drawers and starting to furiously dig through it!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429943700";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299436953";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331905;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331905";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:141:"/me blinks and watches StarOcean go. &quot;Oh uh, if you insist.&quot; and she tries to get up and hang onto StarOcean with her frozen hooves";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429943986";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299439755";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331907;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331907";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:251:"/me rootrootroots, before finally- &quot;Ah hah!&quot; She pulls out some slightly battered spiral ring notebooks in a pack! &quot;I knew i still had some! Here!&quot; She passes them over. &quot;Three empty ones, should hold you over for a bit!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429944057";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299440534";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331915;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331915";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:121:"/me looks up at StarOcean and says &quot;Can I let go?&quot; as frost starts forming slowly on the older pony&#039;s leg.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429944338";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299443275";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331921;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331921";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:123:"/me looks down and sees that, then squeaks and nodnods, eyes wide! &quot;Yesyesyes owwieowwiiiiiiie..!&quot; Cold was cold!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429944420";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299444170";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331922;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331922";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:198:"&quot;Ah! Sorry!&quot; she says, quickly letting go. &quot;Sorry!&quot; she says, putting her hooves under her cloak but then gingerly reaches out for the note book. &quot;T-thank you as vell.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429944467";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299444564";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331923;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331923";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:190:"/me looks at her foreleg in surprise for a few moments.. Then looks back up. &quot;H-How&#039;d you -do- that..?&quot; She looked more curious than anything as she passes the notebooks over.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429944540";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299445367";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331925;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331925";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:223:"/me grimaces and wilts her ears. &quot;I am REALLY very sorry Mis- I mean, Star.&quot; she says with a whimper. &quot;It is very difficult to remember that ponies do not vear warm andfull covering clothes around here.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429944708";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299446980";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331927;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331927";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:262:"&quot;I usually do in the winter,&quot; she replies offhoof, shrugging. She -loved- her full body snowsuit, it was -super- cute! &quot;But still, how&#039;d you do it? I didn&#039;t know ponies did magic just through touch like that!&quot; She was super curious!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429945010";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299450064";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331929;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331929";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:234:"&quot;It is.. a mistake.&quot; she says with a sigh, suddenly curling up a bit on the ground. &quot;I tried to um, imbue my coat... um, my pelt, that is, so that I vould not need to vear the cloak and it... well I cursed myself.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429945140";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299451292";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331933;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331933";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:198:"/me blinkblinks. &quot;O-Oh, wow.. Yeah, that&#039;s not good..&quot; She winces a little. &quot;You make stuff cold when you touch it now?&quot; A very scientific analysis there. &#039;Stuff.&#039;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429945919";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299459157";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331935;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331935";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:364:"/me rubs the back of her neck. &quot;Yes, in a manner of speaking. I think it is something of a um, [i]magical leak[/i] to put it bluntly. I am not sure.. to be honest I have been trying to ignore it. I do not know how to fix it and I am not sure I ever vill.&quot; She breathes a little heavily, her breath making small amounts of fog appear in front of her face.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429946337";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299463265";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331937;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331937";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_