face all up in thought. &quot;I.. Weeeeell.. Maybe some kinda.. What about an amulet that fuels itself on.. Hum..&quot; She was thiiiiiiinking, and an idea was coming together..";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429947415";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299474118";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331964;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331964";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:88:"&quot;Amulet? I am afraid I am not sure I understand.&quot; she says, tilting her head. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429947707";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299476967";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331966;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331966";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:370:"&quot;Don&#039;t get your hopes up, but.. Gimme some time to come up with an idea,&quot; she replies. &quot;The short answer is your curse has gotta be magic, right? If i can make something that runs off of magic, and have it run off of -your- magic, your own curse could power a device that makes your curse not work!&quot; She beams! It was a good theory, at any rate!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429947815";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299478114";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331968;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331968";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:387:"/me holds up her hoof. &quot;I am sorry Star but... the problem is that it is an imbuement written into my skin and bones. Simply depriving it of power vould only be a temporary solution, not to mention it vould prevent me from using any other forms of magick.&quot; She smiles some then and says &quot;However, I vould be happy for you to try. Perhaps ve may both learn something.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429948152";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299481415";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331970;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331970";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:329:"&quot;I don&#039;t like, umm, experimenting on ponies when i can help it..&quot; She replies with a little giggle. &quot;I mean.. It would be fun to just try some simple stuff together, if it&#039;s something so deep then it&#039;d be.. Well, yeah.. Prolly unethical to go -too- crazy..&quot; She did have standards.. Somewhere..";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429948377";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299483738";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331971;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331971";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:176:"&quot;Oh.. vell perhaps ve could have fun anyvay.&quot; she says with a smile &quot;I have never done such things before, so either vay it vould be a learning experience.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429948457";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299484465";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331972;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331972";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"1664";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Portent";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"298";