ight now.&quot; He smiles and offers a hoof. &quot;Portent.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429950291";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299502856";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332001;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332001";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Alraune";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"112";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:53:"/me nods. &quot;Alraune.&quot; She gives a hoof bump.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429950802";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299507856";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332002;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332002";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"1664";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Portent";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"298";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:133:"/me lowers his hoof after the bump. &quot;So, I take it you&#039;re idly wandering too?&quot; he asks. &quot;Want some company?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429951008";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299510034";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332003;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332003";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Alraune";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"112";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:47:"/me shrugs. &quot;Don&#039;t see why not.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429951042";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299510255";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332004;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332004";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"1664";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Portent";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"298";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:241:"/me nods a bit and smiles. &quot;It&#039;s good having someone to talk to on these wanders. I don&#039;t get that too often,&quot; he says, turning to walk alongside Alraune, though he doubted either of them really had a destination in mind.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429951149";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299511439";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332005;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332005";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Alraune";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"112";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:285:"/me did have a reason to be near the train station, but no reason to remain there. She follows along and leads in that meandering we-don&#039;t-care-much-where-we-end-up way. &quot;So... I haven&#039;t seen you around before. I know most of the night ponies. Are you new to town?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429951281";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299512641";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332006;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332006";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"1664";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Portent";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"298";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:224:"/me shrugs a bit. &quot;Eh. Not incredibly new. I just mostly keep to myself. I&#039;m kinda awkward around others usually, don&#039;t really know what to do with myself,&quot; he admits as they wander along directionlessly.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429951395";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299513902";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332007;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332007";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Alraune";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"112";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:57:"/me chuckles. &quot;You&#039;re singin my tune now.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429951430";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299514132";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332008;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332008";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"1664";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Portent";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"298";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:92:"&quot;Ah, not much of a ponies pony yourself?&quot; he asks, casting a quick glance her way.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429951493";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299514878";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332009;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332009";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Alraune";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"112";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:59:"/me shakes her head. &quot;Not really. I hate crowds.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429951519";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299515023";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332010;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332010";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"1664";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Portent";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"298";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:145:"&quot;Hense the night wander? When it&#039;s quiet?&quot; he asks. &quot;I do like the night. It kind of feels roomy, but not really empty.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429951997";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299519924";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#a2b5cd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1332011;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1332011";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"5";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Alraune";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"112";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:181:"/me ponders a moment. &quot;In the daytime, you can see clearly what&#039;s coming a long ways off. I don&#039;t like that. At night anything could happen. It&#039;s exciting!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429952058";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299520413";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}}